## Task 4: Add Proper Schemas

### Required Schemas for Topics

#### 4.1 Article Schema
```typescript
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Article",
  "headline": "...",
  "author": { "@type": "Person", "name": "Mirellé Team" },
  "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Mirellé Inspo" },
  "datePublished": "...",
  "image": "..."
}
```

#### 4.2 FAQPage Schema
```typescript
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "...",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "..."
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

#### 4.3 HowTo Schema (for tutorial topics)
```typescript
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "HowTo",
  "name": "...",
  "step": [
    {
      "@type": "HowToStep",
      "name": "...",
      "text": "...",
      "image": "..."
    }
  ]
}
```

#### 4.4 BreadcrumbList Schema
```typescript
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "..." },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Topics", "item": "..." },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "...", "item": "..." }
  ]
}
```

